snippet.description:
Myself and my Husband welcome you to the Voice's Family. Where we discuss Wrongful Convictions, Domestic Abuse, Murder, Suicide, Depression and more. 
If you or a loved one has a case you would like us to help with As well as, help getting your story out there & heard,  just shoot me a email and we would be happy to check the case out and see what ways we can help you! Im a research assistant for a best selling Author Tania Hagan as well as I help cohost a different channel with my mama and she used to be a PI and D.A  Advocate. This is just one platform within a family of great platforms and TOGETHER, we make a helluva team!
 We may have unpopular opinions and thats okay around here, as long as you can keep it respectful! 
   So buckle up, speakup & ENJOY!
And don't forget -
